data.text:
Comedy couple Paul Scheer and June Diane Raphael have been together for over 10 years – long enough to have had plenty of bad date ideas, secret Chick-fil-A runs (they’re pescetarian), and embarrassing nicknames. But how well do they really know each other? Host Eugene Cordero finds out in this episode of “You Know Me.”
